'''''Cherry Farm''''' is an unpublished [[Wikipedia:Farce|farce]] written by [[J.R.R. Tolkien]] and performed for his [[Incledon family|Incledon relatives]] during part of his vacation at [[Wikipedia:Barnt Green|Barnt Green]] in [[Wikipedia:Worcestershire|Worcestershire]]<ref name=guide>{{CG|RG}}, pg. 75 (entry "Barnt Green (Worcestershire)")</ref> as the seasonal theatrical<ref name=drama>{{CG|RG}}, pg. 226 (entry "Drama - Tolkien as Performer")</ref> on [[Christmas]] in [[1911]].<ref name=chronology>{{CG|C}}, pg. 31 (entry "Christmas 1911")</ref>
